<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link674842" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=674842&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1175933-i-enjoy-reading-about-civil-war-history%2Fanswers%2F674842-it-s-been-a-couple-of">flag</a>
</div>
